00:07:35.476 --> 00:07:37.556 A:middle
supports, these are all still

00:07:37.556 --> 00:07:38.696 A:middle
very important topics to

00:07:38.696 --> 00:07:40.246 A:middle
consider and talk about

00:07:40.526 --> 00:07:41.516 A:middle
throughout the design and

00:07:41.796 --> 00:07:43.726 A:middle
implementation of your app.

00:07:45.376 --> 00:07:47.166 A:middle
So, if all of this is new to

00:07:47.166 --> 00:07:48.226 A:middle
