00:07:48.626 --> 00:07:50.366 A:middle
Like I said before, we have a

00:07:50.406 --> 00:07:52.426 A:middle
great set of APIs that really do

00:07:52.426 --> 00:07:53.716 A:middle
all the heavy lifting for you

00:07:53.716 --> 00:07:54.646 A:middle
and take care of all these

00:07:54.676 --> 00:07:55.516 A:middle
different aspects.

